47 e. The member with experience in nursing home management appointed
48 under G.S. 131E-74.2(b)(2)f.
49 (3) A term of one year:
50 a. The at-large members appointed under G.S. 131E-74.2(b)(1)a.,
51 (b)(2)a., and (b)(2)e.
